          <ul class="type-specs">
            <li><strong>Capacity:</strong> Up to 5,000 lbs</li>
            <li><strong>Use:</strong> Regional routes</li>
            <li><strong>Fleet Size:</strong> 60+ vehicles</li>
          </ul>
