          <ul class="type-specs">
            <li><strong>Temp Range:</strong> -20¬∞F to 60¬∞F</li>
            <li><strong>Use:</strong> Cold chain logistics</li>
            <li><strong>Fleet Size:</strong> 15+ vehicles</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="type-badge">Specialized</span>
        </div>

        <div class="type-card">
          <div class="type-header">
            <span class="type-icon">‚ö°</span>
            <h3>Electric Vehicles</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Zero-emission vehicles for eco-conscious urban delivery solutions.</p>
          <ul class="type-specs">
            <li><strong>Range:</strong> Up to 150 miles</li>
            <li><strong>Use:</strong> Urban eco-delivery</li>
            <li><strong>Fleet Size:</strong> 30+ vehicles</li>
          </ul>
