          </p>
          <div class="tech-features">
            <div class="tech-item">
              <span class="tech-icon">üìç</span>
              <div>
                <h4>GPS Tracking</h4>
                <p>Real-time location tracking for every vehicle in the fleet.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
              <span class="tech-icon">üì±</span>
              <div>
                <h4>Driver Apps</h4>
                <p>Mobile applications for route optimization and delivery confirmation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
              <span class="tech-icon">üîß</span>
              <div>
                <h4>Predictive Maintenance</h4>
                <p>AI-powered systems to prevent breakdowns before they happen.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
              <span class="tech-icon">üìä</span>
              <div>
                <h4>Telematics</h4>
                <p>Advanced data analytics for fleet performance optimization.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-visual">
          <div class="tech-dashboard">
            <div class="dashboard-header">
