              </div>
              <div class="dash-stat">
                <span class="dash-value">98.2%</span>
                <span class="dash-label">Availability</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sustainability -->
  <section class="section sustainability">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Green <span class="text-green">Initiative</span></h2>
        <p>Committed to reducing our environmental footprint.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="green-grid">
        <div class="green-card">
          <span class="green-icon">üå±</span>
          <h4>Carbon Reduction</h4>
          <p>30% reduction in carbon emissions since 2020 through fleet modernization.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="green-card">
          <span class="green-icon">‚ö°</span>
          <h4>Electric Transition</h4>
          <p>40% of our urban fleet now runs on electric or hybrid power.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="green-card">
          <span class="green-icon">‚ôªÔ∏è</span>
          <h4>Sustainable Practices</h4>
          <p>Route optimization reduces fuel consumption by 20% annually.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="green-card">
          <span class="green-icon">üéØ</span>
          <h4>2030 Goal</h4>
          <p>Commitment to 100% carbon-neutral operations by 2030.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Facilities -->
  <section class="section facilities">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our <span class="text-red">Facilities</span></h2>
        <p>Strategic locations to serve you better.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="facility-grid">
        <div class="facility-card">
          <div class="facility-icon">üè≠</div>
          <h4>Distribution Centers</h4>
          <span class="facility-count">8</span>
          <p>Major hubs for sorting and distribution</p>
        </div>
        <div class="facility-card">
          <div class="facility-icon">üì¶</div>
          <h4>Warehouses</h4>
          <span class="facility-count">15</span>
          <p>Secure storage facilities nationwide</p>
        </div>
        <div class="facility-card">
          <div class="facility-icon">üîß</div>
          <h4>Service Centers</h4>
          <span class="facility-count">12</span>
          <p>Fleet maintenance and repair stations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="facility-card">
          <div class="facility-icon">‚ö°</div>
          <h4>Charging Stations</h4>
